{"title":"OnGuard Rock Solid U-Lock Deflects Angle Grinders","link":"https://bikerumor.com/onguard-rock-solid-u-lock/","date":1713624598000,"content":"<p><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-1-1536x1152.jpg\" width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" alt=\"onguard rock solid u-lock with grinder-proof coating\" /></p>\n<p>Coming mid-May, the new OnGuard Rock Solid U-Lock has a 2mm thick diamond ceramic coating that just bounces an angle grinder’s grinding disc off.</p>\n\n\n\n<p>They say the coating is both slick and hard, which won’t let a standard grinding disc penetrate…it just slides. They demonstrated it for quite a while (and had a pile of used discs laying next to it from prior demos) and it showed absolutely no sign of having been cut…or even attempts at cutting it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-2.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-2-1536x1152.jpg\" alt=\"closeup of grinder-proof coating on onguard rock solid u-lock\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-2-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-2-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-2-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-2-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-2.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-3.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-3-1536x1152.jpg\" alt=\"angle grinder trying to cut through the onguard rock solid u-lock\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-3-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-3-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-3-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-3-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-3.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It weighs in at 3lbs, comes with five keys, and includes up to $5,001 of insurance for your bike should someone manage to break it.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-5.jpg\"><img width=\"1536\" height=\"1152\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-5-1536x1152.jpg\" alt=\"packaging for onguard rock solid u-lock\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-5-1536x1152.jpg 1536w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-5-297x223.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-5-120x90.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-5-768x576.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/04/onguard-rock-solid-angle-grinder-proof-bike-u-lock-5.jpg 2000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>MSRP is $199.95.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://onguardlock.com\" target=\"_blank\">OnGuardLocks.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/onguard-rock-solid-u-lock/\">OnGuard Rock Solid U-Lock Deflects Angle Grinders</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"d922a92b63ed7d7db5866e2b7c4f90457d5ba1685b39edb86ce72635c3415970","category":"Cycling"}